Invocation Name: boston city guide
des:
A guide to Boston, Massachusetts; providing an overview and history of the city, as well as places to eat breakfast, lunch, and dinner as well as things to do in the city.

You can ask: 
"Alexa, open Boston City Guide",
"Alexa, ask Boston Guide where I should go"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
